            <lg xml:id="TK578">
<l>karumañ citaiyāmaṟ kaṇṇōṭa vallārk </l>
<l>kurimai yuṭaittiv vulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world is theirs (kings) who are able to show kindness, without injury to their affairs, (administration of justice).</l>
